    <td valign="top" align="left">
		<font face="verdana" size="2">
		<b>Description:</b> <br>
		This is the mother of all direct damage spells! The most powerful direct damage spell in the game. <br>
It does around 1100 Damage.<BR>
<BR>
<B>Research:</B><BR>Rune of Frost, Rune of Astral
		</font>
	 </td>
